thread.title: BRIEF-Bay Bancorp Announces Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.04

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Bay Bancorp Announces Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.04
text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - Bay Bancorp Inc:
* BAY BANCORP, INC. ANNOUNCES YEAR AND FOURTH QUARTER 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.04 * NET INTEREST INCOME FOR THREE-MONTH PERIOD ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2017 TOTALED $6.7 MILLION, COMPARED TO $6.6 MILLION FOR Q3
* BAY BANCORP - NET INTEREST INCOME FOR THREE-MONTH PERIOD ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2017 TOTALED $6.7 MILLION, VERSUS $5.9 MILLION FOR THREE-MONTH PERIOD ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2016â€‹ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
